{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回\"春色透重帘\"主要讲述两条线索交织的故事。第一条线索：李府大厅中，李洛阳、李剑白父子维持秩序，白发老妇人九子鬼母携跛足少年宝儿闯入，向潘乘风索命。跛足少年身手不凡，与霹雳火、黑星天等人交手从容不迫。九子鬼母向众人各赠一粒夺魂珠后离去，众人方知她便是当年一夜毁去祁连派的九子鬼母，九日之内将前来收命。群雄被迫放下恩怨，联手抗敌。第二条线索：铁中棠用珠宝和手段收服了温黛黛，温黛黛抛弃云铮投入铁中棠怀抱。云铮追来对质，遭温黛黛百般羞辱后悲愤离去。铁中棠内心矛盾，既为大旗门大计又对三弟云铮深感愧疚。章末钟声大震，水灵光出现，与温黛黛形成对峙。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黑、白两兄与霹雳大侠之事，与本门无关，亦毋庸在此地解决。三位若愿在此，在下自竭诚款待，三位如定要在外解决，在下恭送如仪，决不相强。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "text": "老夫要走，也不行么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "speaker_name": "李剑白",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "家父话未说完之前，谁也不得妄动。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "text": "你让不让路？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "speaker_name": "李剑白",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "不让！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "借借光好么？让老婆子进去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "text": "有这许多人在这里，你怕什么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "speaker_name": "李剑白",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "老夫人到这里来作甚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "text": "难得难得，老身已有许久未曾见到过像你这样敬老尊贤的人了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "speaker_name": "李剑白",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "此地情况紧急，老夫人无论有什么事，也请稍等再说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "老身要问你讨样东西，你答应么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "老夫人请说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "老身要讨却的东西就是他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "夫人是否在开玩笑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "你答不答应？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "在下实难答应。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "你不答应也得答应。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_bao_er",
      "text": "宝儿，去将那厮脑袋取过来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_er",
      "speaker_name": "跛足少年",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "潘乘风又不是你们的祖宗，小爷要他的脑袋，与你们何干？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_bao_er",
      "text": "小小年纪，就敢如此张狂，老夫如不看在你年纪幼小，就要教训你了，快退回去吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_er",
      "speaker_name": "跛足少年",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "你不妨试试看，看谁教训谁！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_er",
      "speaker_name": "跛足少年",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "来呀，动手呀！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_bao_er",
      "text": "老夫生平不与妇人童子交手。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_er",
      "speaker_name": "跛足少年",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "既不动手，还站在这里干什么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_bao_er",
      "text": "小兄弟，你和这位潘大侠究竟有何仇恨，为何定要他的脑袋呢？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_er",
      "speaker_name": "跛足少年",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "你管不着。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_bao_er",
      "text": "在李大哥的地方，什么事自有李大哥处理，在下自然是管不着。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_er",
      "speaker_name": "跛足少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最好谁也不要多管闲事。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "潘乘风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都不管了么？难道不怕我说出来？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "潘乘风",
      "listener": "char_bao_er",
      "text": "黑星天、司徒笑，还不来助我一臂？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": "char_bao_er",
      "text": "我来助你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "李大哥，你说得厉害，怎么又不管了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "出去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "你叫老身出去么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "带着你的孙儿立时出去，远离李宅。你纵要寻仇，也不能在李宅方圆一里之内动手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "你若要多事，就要后悔了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "李洛阳纵然拼却这份身家，拼却这条性命，也不能让你们坏了我家的规矩。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "好个执迷不悟的蠢才，若是家毁人亡了，还要那规矩有什么用？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "要我李洛阳家毁人亡，还不是那么轻易的事，阁下尽管放心好了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_bao_er",
      "text": "宝儿，住手了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宝儿，我们争吵了半日，也该给人家留下些什么。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_er",
      "speaker_name": "跛足少年",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "师傅，这少年也莫要送了，好么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": "char_bao_er",
      "text": "你倒小气得很。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_er",
      "speaker_name": "跛足少年",
      "listener": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "text": "我才不小气呢！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_zi_gui_mu",
      "speaker_name": "白发老妇人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "礼送完了，我们也要走了，九日之内，我们来收人家的回礼。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "潘乘风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夺魂珠……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那两人装模作样，究竟在弄什么鬼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "潘乘风",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "一粒明珠一条命，得了珠子的人，九日之内，她便要来要你的命了！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "text": "他们到底是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "潘乘风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还猜不出她是谁么？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "潘乘风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们难道都猜不出她是谁么？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她便是九子鬼母？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，她便是一夜之间，毁去了祁连派数十个弟子的九子鬼母。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "潘乘风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夺魂珠一到，我们谁也逃不了，海大少呀海大少，想不到你也要陪我死在一起！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "text": "谁也逃脱不了？九子鬼母再厉害也不过是个人而已，难道她真的是活鬼么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当年祁连派那等声势，接到夺魂珠后，九日之内，竟无一人能逃得出祁连山庄，幸好……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "text": "剑白，你快快随着霹雳大侠去吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "text": "数日之内，这里便成血海，你还是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_jian_bai",
      "speaker_name": "李剑白",
      "listener": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "text": "爹爹若是要孩儿离开此地，孩儿便立刻自刎在爹爹面前！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好男儿，有志气！老夫也不走了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_luo_yang",
      "speaker_name": "李洛阳",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "兄台既是脱身事外，还是快走的好，到那时变乱一起，玉石俱焚，兄台再走便来不及了！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黑星天、白星武纵然不义，但老夫也不能眼见他们死于别人手中，袖手不管，好歹也要助他们与别人拼上一场，纵然拼不过，纵然死了，也得成全这一场义气。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "text": "但此事过后，你我三人若还不死，老夫还是要来找你们的。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "潘乘风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正该如此。你我此刻已有如身在危城，自应同心合力，对付外敌，自身的恩怨，还管他作甚？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "text": "若是没有你这厮，怎会有今日之事？你莫要以为大乱一起，你便可浑水摸鱼，这笔账还是要找你算的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "潘乘风",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "此事过了，我也一定等着你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "speaker_name": "水灵光",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "这是我亲手做的，你要吃下它。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我准时来了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你那汉子知道么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "那盒首饰……可在这里么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "就在这里。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "好……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你做什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你要的是我的身子，我就把身子给你。你得到了我的身子，也该将我要的东西给我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "这交易就如此简单么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你还要什么？难道这还不够？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "换那套首饰，是足够了，但……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "这些都是你的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "自然都是我的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你真是福气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "这些你想要么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你都给我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你愿意永远跟着我，我就都给你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我不能，我不能……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你可以考虑考虑。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你考虑过了么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我不能！",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "不能就算了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你不给我，难道我就不会动手抢么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "这是什么地方，你敢？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我抢了你，也没有人知道。这是你逼我的，你莫要怪我。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你敢，看你还敢不敢？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你愿意么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你愿意永远地跟着我么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你是否愿意放弃一切跟着我？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "愿意。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "贱妇，我早就知道你愿意跟着我，只因我不但能给你珠宝，满足你的虚荣，还能满足你的无耻！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你若是愿意，就快些回去告诉那少年，对他说你以后永远不要再见他的面了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "贱人，你究竟愿不愿意？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我去了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "快去快回，天亮前定要回来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹。你能原谅孩儿所用的手段么？孩儿自己也不知是不是对的！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你告别了你那汉子么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你做事倒也干净利落得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我是自由的身子，来去谁管得着我？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "那少年难道也就如此简单地让你走么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "他凭什么不让我走？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你难道与他没有一丝情感？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我会爱他？那孩子连牙齿都没有长全……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "他难道也与你没有情感？我就不信他肯如此轻易地……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "黛黛，你在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你到底和他说清了没有？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "黛黛在这里。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "这是别人的地方，谁叫你进来的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "我来找你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "有何贵干？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "这……这是你写的么？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "不是我写的，难道还会是你写的不成？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "我心已有别属，难再与君共处，我去了，但望你莫来寻我，我也不愿与君再见……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "这些话，真的都是你写的？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "对了，这都是我写的，写得清清楚楚，你还不明白？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你……你要离开我，跟着这……老头子？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "他说你是个老头子，我却说你是个男人，真正的男人，比那些乳臭未干的小伙子，不知要强多少倍。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你以前和我的山誓海盟，难道都是……都是……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "那都是和小孩子说着玩的话，你难道也会将它当做真的，这倒可笑得很！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "不不不，那都是真的，你……你绝对不会骗我，黛黛，你……你跟我回去吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "随你回去，随你回去做什么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "亏你算得堂堂七尺，看来也有三分像是个男人，怎的做事竟这么幼稚，这么无耻。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "人家厌恶你，不喜欢你了，你却偏偏要作出这么可笑的样子，真叫人看了心里发呕。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "放开手，出去！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "这里是老夫的地方，你话若说完了，就请快出去吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "主人已在赶你出去，你还呆在这里？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你用钱买去了她，总有一天，她也会……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "要是被人赶出去，那可真是光荣极了，你死在地下的祖宗八代，都要沾你的光。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，你们记得……你们记得……总有一天……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "蠢才！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我已完全是你的了！你！你还不过来……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "清晨之中，警钟大鸣，莫非这里又出了什么事么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "粉衣艳婢",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你既已是这里的人，还不过来参拜我家姑娘。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "她是什么人？要我拜她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "这是舍妹，你……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "她是你的妹妹？嘿嘿！这倒妙极了，六十岁的男人，也会有十多岁的妹妹？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 640
    }
